<span id="freeTextContainer17146838925385658128">What I liked: The reassurance that air travel is very safe. Big decisions should be emotional decisions. The author is wearing a hoodie in his picture (he better like drinking beer).<br/>What I didn&apos;t like: The use of monkeys in experiments. Super sad!<br/>Who I&apos;d suggest it to: Anyone who likes pretending they are a psychologist. This will add more ammunition to the psychological gun.</span>
